import React from 'react'
import Hero from '../Components/Hero'
import Navbar from '../Components/Navbar'
import AboutImg from "../assets/1.jpg"

const About = () => {
  return (
    <>
          <Navbar/>
        <Hero
           cName="hero-mid"
           heroimage={AboutImg}
           title="About"
        />

    </>
  )
}

export default About
